p: In the District Court of Washington Territory and for the 4th Judicial District thereof, holding terms at County court of Spokane County Territory of Washington vs. Ray Raymond Deft. Territory of Washington County of Spokane}ss B.C. Nan Houston being by one first duly sworn says that he is the auditor of Spokane County Washington Territory and that the foregoing list of persons qualified to act as Grandy Juror in the duly dist. filed in his office for the year of 1887, and that the said foregoing writ a true and correct copy of the the onsaid writ in my office and the manner and in the same on not the original and that the grand jury for the May term of the District Court of said County was reelected from said writ. B.C. VanHouston Subscribed & sworn to before me this the 23rd day of May 1887. A. T. Barns Notary Public
